				<h2 class="heading--2">Facing the Challenges of Implementing a Continuous Risk Management Program</h2>

				<p class="paragraph--2">The need to optimize the security program is especially vital, considering Etisalat’s recent and projected expansion. For years, Etisalat’s security teams relied heavily on open source security tools to identify vulnerabilities, as well as many of the benchmarking tools and checklists provided by The SANS Institute and The CERT Coordination Center, in addition to customized checklists to help them quantify and manage their IT risks.</p>
